  "body": "Network - Ethereum Mainnet\r\n\r\nErigon version: `./erigon/2.28.1`\r\n\r\nOS & Version: linux-amd64\r\n\r\n When calling ```trace_call``` with an extremely large value, passing in the ```stateDiff``` parameter, we expect the response to be ```\"insufficient funds for transfer:’``` or similar. \r\n\r\nInstead, the response returns incorrect data. \r\n\r\nCurl command to reproduce:\r\n```\r\ncurl -X POST   'localhost:8545'   --header 'Content-Type: application/json'   --data '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"trace_call\",\"params\":[{\"from\":\"0xc1f02f43d8c0aede650aecca29a94e9498b30286\",\"to\":\"0x07bb7a938f4ac7043c3127513a910599ca88ea06\", \"gas\": \"0x5208\", \"gasPrice\": \"0x21faec1933\", \"value\": \"0x1456f22c1aee9000000000000000000000000\"},[\"trace\", \"stateDiff\"],\"latest\"],\"id\":1}'|jq\r\n```\r\n\r\nActual Output:\r\n```\r\n{\r\n  \"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n  \"id\": 1,\r\n  \"result\": {\r\n    \"output\": \"0x\",\r\n    \"stateDiff\": {\r\n      \"0x07bb7a938f4ac7043c3127513a910599ca88ea06\": {\r\n        \"balance\": {\r\n          \"*\": {\r\n            \"from\": \"0x96c404020e4000\",\r\n            \"to\": \"0x1456f22c1aee9000000000096c404020e4000\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        \"code\": \"=\",\r\n        \"nonce\": \"=\",\r\n        \"storage\": {}\r\n      },\r\n      \"0xc1f02f43d8c0aede650aecca29a94e9498b30286\": {\r\n        \"balance\": \"=\",\r\n        \"code\": \"=\",\r\n        \"nonce\": {\r\n          \"*\": {\r\n            \"from\": \"0x67\",\r\n            \"to\": \"0x68\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        \"storage\": {}\r\n      },\r\n      \"0xf2f5c73fa04406b1995e397b55c24ab1f3ea726c\": {\r\n        \"balance\": {\r\n          \"*\": {\r\n            \"from\": \"0x204edb4a833651e1\",\r\n            \"to\": \"0x20582c3bfd4c05d9\"\r\n          }\r\n        },\r\n        \"code\": \"=\",\r\n        \"nonce\": \"=\",\r\n        \"storage\": {}\r\n      }\r\n    },\r\n    \"trace\": [\r\n      {\r\n        \"action\": {\r\n          \"from\": \"0xc1f02f43d8c0aede650aecca29a94e9498b30286\",\r\n          \"callType\": \"call\",\r\n          \"gas\": \"0x0\",\r\n          \"input\": \"0x\",\r\n          \"to\": \"0x07bb7a938f4ac7043c3127513a910599ca88ea06\",\r\n          \"value\": \"0x1456f22c1aee9000000000000000000000000\"\r\n        },\r\n        \"result\": {\r\n          \"gasUsed\": \"0x0\",\r\n          \"output\": \"0x\"\r\n        },\r\n        \"subtraces\": 0,\r\n        \"traceAddress\": [],\r\n        \"type\": \"call\"\r\n      }\r\n    ],\r\n    \"vmTrace\": null\r\n  }\r\n}\r\n```\r\nExpected Output (taken from a Nethermind Node):\r\n```\r\n{\r\n\"jsonrpc\": \"2.0\",\r\n\"error\": {\r\n  \"code\": -32000,\r\n  \"message\": \"insufficient funds for transfer: address 0xc1f02f43d8c0aede650aecca29a94e9498b30286\"\r\n},\r\n\"id\": 1\r\n}\r\n```\r\n",
